name: Work From Home - Illustration Kit
description:
Built for the First Ever Figma Portugal Meetup, this illustration library is a complete set of characters and objects for you to replicate your Home Office space.

Well, not exclusivelly. Use it for whatever you feel like!

This verson 1.0 includes:
- A character builder
- Furniture
- Lighthing
- Plants
- Devices and Gadgets
- Objects
- Windows
- A pair of easter eggs
